abla f(\mathbf{x}) = \left[  egin{array}{c} 2(x_1 - 2) \ 2x_2 \end{array} ight] \] \[ \mathbf{g}(\mathbf{x}) = \left[  egin{array}{c} x_1 - x_2 + 2 \ -x_1^2 + x_2 - 1 \ x_1 \ x_2 \end{array} ight] \] \[ 
abla \mathbf{g}(\mathbf{x}) = \left[  egin{array}{cccc} 1 &amp; -2x_1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \ -1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 \end{array} ight] \] <p>列出题目条件</p> \[  egin{align} 
abla f(x^*) - 
abla h(x^*) y^* - 
abla g(x^*) \mu^* = 0 \end{align} \] \[ \Longrightarrow \left[  egin{array}{c} 2(x_1 - 2) \ 2x_2 \end{array} ight] - \left[  egin{array}{cccc} 1 &amp; -2x_1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \ -1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 \end{array} ight] \left[  egin{array}{c} \mu_1 \ \mu_2 \ \mu_3 \ \mu_4 \end{array} ight] = \left[  egin{array}{c} 0 \ 0 \end{array} ight] \] \[ \mu^* \otimes g(x^*) = 0 \quad \Longrightarrow \left[  egin{array}{c} \mu_1 (x_1 - x_2 + 2) \ \mu_2 (-x_1^2 + x_2 - 1) \ \mu_3 x_1 \ \mu_4 x_2 \end{array} ight] = 0 \] \[ g(x^*) \ge 0 \quad \mu^* \ge 0 \] <p>得出方程</p> \[  egin{align} 2(x_1 - 2) - \mu_1 + 2 \mu_2 x_1 - \mu_3 = 0 \ 2x_2 + \mu_1 - \mu_2 - \mu_4 = 0 \ \mu_1 (x_1 - x_2 + 2) = 0 \ \mu_2 (-x_1^2 + x_2 - 1) = 0 \ \mu_3 x_1 = 0 \ \mu_4 x_2 = 0 \ \mu_j \ge 0 \quad j = 1, 2, 3, 4 \ x_2 \le x_1 + 2 \ x_2 \ge x_1^2 + 1 \ x_1, x_2 \ge 0 \end{align} \] <p>求解方程 观察可得：\(\mu_1 = \mu_3 = \mu_4 = 0\)（松弛性）</p> <p>所以有：</p> \[ (1 + \mu_2) x_1 - 2 = 0 \] \[ 2x_2 - \mu_2 = 0 \] \[ -x_1^2 + x_2 - 1 = 0 \] <p>求解得：</p> \[ \mu_2^* = 2.6219 \quad x_1^* = 0.5536 \quad x_2^* = 1.3064 \] \[ f(x^*) = 3.7989 \]

